<paragraph id="801140617A877B8C01510A270E4231CE" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Endemic in the Philippines. Luzon Island, Zambales Province, Municipalities of Sta. Cruz and Candelaria.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="55BE1731F731B513B140D12569E1147E" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="habitat and ecology">
<paragraph id="85929B513D84E93840C7FBCA2F8424C8" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Habitat and ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="66D27F6D7527F0DDB9CD149484FD8448" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
